Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的舞台是鹿兒鳥鹿兒島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔瘋狂迷戀日本燒酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  之幽香  人之百態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.80,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,470)}麴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起酒的話首先聯想到的就是啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.00,0:02:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝上這麼一大杯冰凍的啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這更享受的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.70,0:02:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其魅力當然源自於它特有的苦澀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.40,0:02:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們想瞭解的不是啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們邀請我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為我一碰上酒的話題就會侃侃而談嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請就目前最受歡迎的一種酒發表一下您的高見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  說到葡萄酒的魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是葡萄酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在如此重要的觀眾點播的特別節目裡 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他腦袋怎麼一點也不開竅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是個相當有知名度的嗜酒族才請他來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.20,0:02:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到鹿兒島的酒應該一下就反應過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主持人姐姐已經哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有股殺氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經來到鹿兒島了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿兒島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到鹿兒島的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒很好喝  葡萄酒也很好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我最喜歡喝的還是日本燒酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.90,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於還沒有認識到日本燒酒的美味的人我深表遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以您才故意提及其它的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.70,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究騙不過大家  我毛利小五郎也不再隱瞞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒酒中尤其是貴寶地鹿兒島的燒酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.00,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的薩摩燒酒 美味至極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿兒島  萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生  精彩極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是找對人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算矇混過關了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他的強項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說高隈  是那個夢幻般的燒酒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  完全是限量產的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難到手  絕對是極品中的極品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.90,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能品嚐到如此的美酒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們拜託了當地作坊的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說非常樂意招待毛利先生 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.00,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘船從鹿兒島到正對面的垂水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.50,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做夢都想喝那夢幻般的高隈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們便走進了那樁即將發生的可怕的事件之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.70,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉倒在薩摩的小五郎 前篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高隈釀酒  酒就是從這兒釀造出來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原來以為是一個更大的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.00,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡真漂亮  正對著大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生  這位是作坊的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此唐突實在很抱歉  我是毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您來  我是白石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久仰大名  我是白石的妻子扶美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我女兒小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有寄宿在我家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.10,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟你們對釀酒不太感興趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是高隈山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  作坊名就是取自那兒的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家進屋再聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.90,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高隈酒的味道如何 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了說它美味沒有什麼好形容的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是普通的酒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.60,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  這是極品  美妙絕倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雖然只是普普通通的釀酒工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卻一直引以為豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釀酒的一系列工序從蒸熟洗淨的大米開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後摻入??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.00,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,470)}麴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(384,470)}菌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著將米糊倒入釀造桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入水和酵母進行發酵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.50,0:06:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後加入蒸好的紅薯繼續發酵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這期間為了保持穩定的溫度  不讓雜菌繁殖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用木棒不停地攪拌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後蒸餾  候熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才算大功告成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人提出用機器進行大批量生產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們還是堅持手工釀造而否定了那種提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.40,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限量生產聽起來像做秀一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是釀造不了那麼多 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.30,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要釀一點實實在在的東西  現在已經是極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真正手工釀造的酒才好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是前兩天提出採訪要求的週刊雜誌的前園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常務的辰村先生要我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  當聽到辰村的名字後突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我拍攝釀酒的工序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釀酒工序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生同意了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.90,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨隨便便就同意愚蠢的採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  釀酒工序是無法讓外人觀看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於釀酒來說  外部混入的雜菌是大忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以釀酒過程中除了釀酒師以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  人身上的確有許多雜菌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很喜歡燒酒所以就接受了採訪的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連這些都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是對你發脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對那個常務辰村感到惱火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎大聲嚷嚷啊  小杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太受歡迎嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是前園小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.50,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的那個健康檢查沒想到花了不少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.60,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這麼狹小的釀酒作坊你很吃驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我正打算擴建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用機器  就可以大批量生產了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高隈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大批量生產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生  不是一直說不考慮這事的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大批量生產的話  質量一定會下降的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  社長是個死腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趁著這股燒酒之風好好賺它一筆怎麼行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為大批量生產不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會重新考慮是否進行採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我們也很希望能做一下宣傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不更加愛惜自己作坊釀造出來的酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜破壞高隈酒的美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們也該回去工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些使酒腐敗的雜菌就算沒有從外部混入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也早就進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.40,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜菌 是說我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒一個好東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄一直以來堅持的手工釀酒法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 今天多謝款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  是那個名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人再合適不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做你們產品的形象代言人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找了好久了  一位合適的名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.00,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您能接受的話我們的酒您要多少給多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高隈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對酒的抵抗力實在太差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  明天帶您參觀一下附近的景致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好休息  還可品味美味佳餚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您一定接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生  如果可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白石太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這麼喜歡我們的酒是我們的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必讓我做您的導遊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由女性陪伴更為愉快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託白石太太了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依舊過一個慵懶的休息日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生  我等候您的答覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  為什麼不明確地拒絕他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.10,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是西鄉隆盛  好威武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就轉移話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個辰村先生的確讓人感覺很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像也不太喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是討厭  而是憎惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼白石夫婦還會繼續僱用他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是櫻島上空的風向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.20,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿兒島的天氣預報裡還有櫻島上空的風向啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有什麼用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有火山灰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻島上的火山灰會隨風飄散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吹到晾曬的衣服上就會很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要播報風向情況啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會有火山灰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很任性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  怎麼寫上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.60,0:12:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不解雇那個叫辰村的叔叔呢 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  連小孩子也會感到奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們不能解雇辰村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他從前對我們有恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有恩於你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的作坊也有一定的歷史了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但終究是一個沒有名氣的小作坊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釀造出來的酒也沒有什麼銷路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來早就該倒閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使它維持到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠負責銷售的辰村先生不辭辛勞地四處推銷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.10,0:13:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是始終無法與薄利多銷的大型生產商抗衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於快倒閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.10,0:13:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是十年前  也就是我嫁入白石家五年前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的作坊主人白石的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和還在學習的我的丈夫做出了一個決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是最後一次了  就按照自己的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最嚴格的原料和釀造工藝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釀造出最棒的酒來為高隈作坊謝幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是高隈酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  純正的酒得到了大家的認可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在期待純正的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在去年冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸由於積勞成疾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要忘了十年前的決心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.50,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起  辰村先生就變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  大批量生產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在顧客都是衝著高隈酒的牌子來買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算味道有點變樣  大家也不會介意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做生意  做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放任他這樣肆無忌憚嗎 社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果敢打酒的主意  就把他踢出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.90,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為有他我們的作坊才沒有倒閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的恩德  我一生都不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公他就是那麼頑固  死腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永生不忘所受之恩  薩摩男人的作風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很講義氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必拒絕昨天辰村先生拜託您的事 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有毛利先生這樣的名人鼎力宣傳的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.40,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於辰村先生來說好比如虎添翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.10,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會強行建議批准機械化大批量生產的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.70,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天來當導遊的目的就是為了說服我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.80,0:15:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就打算拒絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生的房子在鹿兒島市的市中心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  他好像在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生成家了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有  他一個人生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先進去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生  我是白石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有覺得嘴裡沙沙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是吹過火山灰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白石太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是辰村先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以想像所發生的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生在休息日小憩的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現場情況來分析  很明顯是被綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來到這裡的時候房裡的燈亮著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明是在傍晚時分被綁架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯案時間可以更精確一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我檢查現場的時候血跡還未干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這起案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我們到達這裡的6點前沒多久犯下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大竹山  用警車實行緊急追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.90,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.50,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那位女士  您之前是中央醫院的護士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.20,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一直到五年前結婚為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  果然是那時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭什麼  快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.90,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們也捲入案件實在很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有些不好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但辰村先生畢竟曾是作坊的恩人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了金錢作案的話犯人一定會提出要求的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時便會露出狐狸尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是直到第二天也沒有犯人的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聯絡我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又過了一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縣警署接到一個匿名電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.60,0:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在鹿兒島市內的寺山公園裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方很少有人經過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話來的人應該就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說聲音經過處理無法辨別男女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架後再殺人嗎  到底是什麼樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了兩天了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.20,0:19:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體解剖的結果是兩天前  也就是那天遇害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經過了兩天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法估計準確的死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那天傍晚至夜裡遇害這一點是錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是頭部受鈍器襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擊斃命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在客廳的那個裝飾品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的凹凸裂痕與死者傷口完全吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.90,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  所沾的血跡也已斷定系辰村先生的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以確定它就是凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.50,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擊斃命的話  說明犯人不是把他打暈再帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是當場將其殺害並搬離現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把屍體和汽車一起丟棄在公園裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天後的今天  再特地來告訴我們遺棄的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要把屍體從那幢房子搬出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還來告訴我們他遺棄的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.10,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  根據鑒定報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰村先生的房門和所有窗戶都沒有被撬過的痕跡  
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.00,0:20:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房子的鑰匙是特製的  無法配備用鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼犯人是如何進屋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說犯人是辰村先生認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這案件沒有財產損失所以不是搶劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠想到的只有仇殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對辰村先生恨之入骨而且是他身邊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.40,0:21:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對辰村先生懷有敵意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個釀酒作坊的人以外沒有其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.20,0:21:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼連我也成了嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.60,0:21:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在錄口供時得知你對辰村先生懷有敵意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然恨他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.50,0:21:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家都是如此  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在前天傍晚被殺的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.80,0:21:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我們大家都在作坊裡釀酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.90,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是說了嗎  大家都在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.80,0:21:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能排除你們大傢俬下對口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.80,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有前園小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.60,0:21:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說當時一個人在旅館的房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.40,0:21:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的不在場證明也不成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想懷疑大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是新福警官的話不無道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.60,0:22:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的任何人都沒有確實的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且誰都憎恨辰村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.00,0:22:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白石太太很痛苦吧  身邊的人都遭懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.50,0:22:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  犯人說不定就在這些人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.90,0:24:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒是有生命的  必須有人照看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.00,0:24:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  難得能在大家面前表現一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.20,0:24:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.60,0:24:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉倒在薩摩的小五郎 後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.70,0:24:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.80,0:24:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健康檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.10,0:24:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是鹿兒鳥解決篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.30,0:24:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要喝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.30,0:24:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
